author: marvin
msg: Force the "cnick" for the Clownfish parcel KinoSearch to "Lucy", by hacking
the Clownfish compiler.  This changes the prefixes for all C symbols within
the parcel from kino_/Kino_/KINO_ to lucy_/Lucy_/LUCY_, without changing the
layout of the files or the class names.  While this is a large patch, aside
from the Clownfish hack, it was an entirely mechanical substitution.
